Variable.Name: CRM_SCRIPTS_Dashboard_Search_Employee
Variable.Value:
<script>
document.addEventListener('DataPageReady', function(event) {
    var interval = setInterval(function() {
        var employeeDropdown = document.querySelector('select[name$="Virtual2"]');
        employeeDropdown.value = '[@eid]';
        if (employeeDropdown.value == '[@eid]') {
            clearInterval(interval);
        };
    }, 1000);
});
</script>

Variable.Name: CRM_SCRIPTS_Role_Change
Variable.Value:
<script>
    var interval = setInterval(function() {
        var role = document.querySelector('select[name$="Role"]').value;
        if (role == 'EMP') {
            var dropdown = document.querySelector('select[name$="Virtual3"]');
            var managerID = '[@field:ManagerID]';
            if (managerID == 0) {
                clearInterval(interval);
            } else {
                dropdown.value = managerID;
                if (dropdown.value == managerID) {
                    clearInterval(interval);
                };
            }
        } else {
            clearInterval(interval);
        };
    }, 1500);
</script>

Variable.Name: CRM_SCRIPTS_Search_Button
Variable.Value:
<script>
       var searchButton = document.querySelector('input[type="submit"]');
       searchButton.parentElement.style.display = 'none';
       document.getElementById('searchButton').addEventListener('click', function() {
            searchButton.click();
        });
       document.getElementById('searchButton').classList.add('mb-2')
       document.getElementById('searchButton').classList.add('mt-2')
       document.querySelector('a > button.cbSearchButton').classList.add('mt-2')
       document.querySelector('a > button.cbSearchButton').classList.add('mb-2')
</script>
